{"lastModified":1764343647732,"uri":"c::7580663817::vessel::d5cca39b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer Operating Area: USA - New England\nWinter Operating Area: Bahamas\n\nTAHINA is a 15.24m / 50ft Catamaran Luxury Yacht built in 2008 by St. Francis and later underwent a refit in 2021. Sleeping 6 guests in 3 cabins and with a crew of 2. Cruising at 7.00 kn/ph with a top speed of 10.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprise of 2 cabins with a queen size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities, and a cabin with a double bed and a pullman bed and en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"TAHINA","images":["/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cca39b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::11291700-aa82-11ee-b137-636a424dbccc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cca39b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fd8ea070-aa81-11ee-b137-636a424dbccc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cca39b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::112aebc0-aa82-11ee-b137-636a424dbccc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cca39b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fd8fd8f0-aa81-11ee-b137-636a424dbccc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cca39b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fd907530-aa81-11ee-b137-636a424dbccc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cca39b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::07e0d6b0-aa82-11ee-b137-636a424dbccc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cca39b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::0b693a20-aa82-11ee-b137-636a424dbccc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cca39b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::0b6b0ee0-aa82-11ee-b137-636a424dbccc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cca39b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1129da50-aa82-11ee-b137-636a424dbccc.jpeg/{imageVaria